---
// src/components/UnfairAdvantage.astro
---
<section id="how-it-works" class="py-24 bg-white relative overflow-hidden">
    <style>
        @keyframes fadeInUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(10px); }
            to { opacity: 1; transform: translateY(0); }
        }
        @keyframes float {
            0%, 100% { transform: translateY(0px); }
            50% { transform: translateY(-10px); }
        }
        .animate-reveal {
            opacity: 0; /* Start hidden */
            animation: fadeInUp 0.8s ease-out forwards; /* Run animation */
        }
        .animate-floating {
            animation: float 6s ease-in-out infinite;
        }
    </style>

    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-2 gap-16 items-center">
            
            <div>
                <h2 class="text-4xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-8 tracking-tight text-display">
                    Stop shouting from a rooftop. <br>
                    <span class="text-blue-600">Start knocking on doors.</span>
                </h2>
                
                <div class="text-lg text-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-10">
                    <p class="mb-6">
                        Think of your current website like renting a massive billboard on the <strong class="text-slate-900">Federal Highway</strong>. It costs a fortune, it's noisy, and most people drive right past it without looking.
                    </p>
                    
                    <p class="mb-4 font-semibold text-slate-900">
                        Stegg changes the game. We chop that one expensive billboard into 50 localized signposts:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="space-y-4">
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <div class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <span>
                                <strong>Target patients, not traffic:</strong> If you run a <strong class="text-slate-900">Premium Skin Clinic</strong> in Bangsar, we digitally plant flags in elite residential areas like <em>Damansara Heights, Bukit Tunku, and Sri Hartamas</em>.
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <div class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <span>
                                <strong>Be the trusted business:</strong> When a customer in <strong class="text-slate-900">Damansara Heights</strong> searches for a facial treatment, they don't see a generic "KL" ad. They see "Top Rated Skin Clinic Damansara Heights".
                            </span>
                        </li>
                        <li class="flex gap-3">
                            <div class="mt-2 w-1.5 h-1.5 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex-shrink-0"></div>
                            <span>
                                <strong>Win the high-value appointment:</strong> People trust businesses that feel local and convenient. They book with you first.
                            </span>
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                </div>

                <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4">
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-slate-50 rounded-xl border border-slate-100 w-full sm:w-auto">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-red-100 flex items-center justify-center text-red-600 shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="map" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">The Old Way</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Hoping patients find you.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="flex items-center gap-3 p-4 bg-blue-50 rounded-xl border border-blue-100 w-full sm:w-auto">
                        <div class="w-10 h-10 rounded-full bg-blue-600 flex items-center justify-center text-white shrink-0">
                            <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-5 h-5"></i>
                        </div>
                        <div>
                            <div class="font-bold text-slate-900 text-sm">The Stegg Way</div>
                            <div class="text-xs text-slate-500">Going to where they live.</div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <div class="relative">
                <div class="absolute -inset-4 bg-gradient-to-tr from-slate-100 to-white rounded-3xl transform rotate-3"></div>
                <div class="relative bg-white rounded-2xl shadow-xl border border-slate-100 overflow-hidden animate-floating">
                    <div class="bg-slate-900 px-6 py-4 flex items-center justify-between">
                        <span class="text-white font-bold">The "Google Search" Reality</span>
                        <div class="flex gap-1.5">
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></div>
                            <div class="w-2.5 h-2.5 rounded-full bg-slate-700"></div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="divide-y divide-slate-100">
                        <div class="p-6 hover:bg-slate-50 transition-colors animate-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.2s;">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="mt-1"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase">Patient Types:</span></div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">"Skin Specialist <span class="text-red-500 line-through decoration-2">Kuala Lumpur</span>"</div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-500 mt-1">Too broad. You compete with 200 other clinics.</p>
                                    <div class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-red-500 bg-red-50 px-2 py-1 rounded"><i data-lucide="thumbs-down" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Hard to rank</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-blue-50/30 animate-reveal" style="animation-delay: 0.8s;">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="mt-1"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase">Patient Types:</span></div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">"Acne Treatment <span class="text-blue-600 font-bold bg-blue-100 px-1 rounded">Damansara Heights</span>"</div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">"This clinic is nearby." High intent. Easy win.</p>
                                    <div class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2 py-1 rounded"><i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Stegg ranks here easily</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <div class="p-6 bg-cyan-50/30 animate-reveal" style="animation-delay: 1.4s;">
                            <div class="flex items-start gap-4">
                                <div class="mt-1"><span class="text-xs font-bold text-slate-400 uppercase">Patient Types:</span></div>
                                <div>
                                    <div class="text-lg font-medium text-slate-900">"Pico Laser <span class="text-cyan-600 font-bold bg-cyan-100 px-1 rounded">Mont Kiara</span>"</div>
                                    <p class="text-sm text-slate-600 mt-1">Wealthy neighborhood. Ready to book now.</p>
                                    <div class="mt-2 inline-flex items-center gap-1 text-xs font-bold text-blue-600 bg-blue-100 px-2 py-1 rounded"><i data-lucide="trophy" class="w-3 h-3"></i> Stegg ranks here too</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                    <div class="bg-slate-50 p-4 text-center border-t border-slate-100 z-10 relative">
                        <p class="text-xs text-slate-500 font-medium">We auto-generate pages for <strong>every</strong> affluent neighborhood.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>